            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1712223754,
            "creation_date": 1712210839,
            "body": "<p>Updating to latest Android Studio Iguana can help you to fix this issue if your app is targeting Android 14 (sdk 34).<\/p>\n<p>I'm not sure about the reason of this bug. But my app was targeting Android SDK 34, but I was using old version of Android studio (Electric Eel) which was creating this crash about dex. I updated the Studio and issue resolved.<\/p>\n<p>Note- Don't forget to uninstall and install again.<\/p>\n",
